    "To address this inherent unpredictability, we conducted multiple queries for each harmful input as a countermeasure.",
    "Furthermore, in the context of knowledge distillation, we limited our selection to four models during our process, recognizing that alternative models may outperform them.",
    "Our research primarily investigates the effectiveness of knowledge distillation in enhancing testing efficiency rather than determining optimal model selections.",
    "Consequently, our approach may require additional validation and adaptation when applied to different LLMs or other prospective models considered in future research.",
